definitions.definition: One more further, in addition to the quantity by then; a second or additional one, similar in likeness or in effect.
examples: Yes, I'd like another slice of cake, thanks.
Do you know another way to do this job?

definitions.definition: Any or some other, similar in likeness or in effect, instead.
examples: One gold ingot is valued the same as another , but gemstones are valued individually.

main_definition: One more further, in addition to the quantity by then; a second or additional one, similar in likeness or in effect.
secondary_definitions: Any or some other, similar in likeness or in effect, instead.
